## Diagram 4: ICP/VDIP Calculation Flow

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph INPUT["📥 Input Data (PeopleFluent)"]
        GRANT["ICP Grant<br/>Employee × Grant_Year<br/>× Fund_Type"]
        VEST_SCH["Vesting Schedule<br/>TR_1=20%, TR_2=20%<br/>TR_3=20%, TR_4=20%<br/>TR_5=20%"]
        ROR["RoR Assumption<br/>PI Fund: 10%<br/>Total Fund: 7%"]
        FORF["Forfeiture Rate<br/>3%–5% per annum"]
    end

    subgraph CALC["🔧 ICP Calculation Engine (Groovy)"]
        direction TB
        STEP1["Step 1: Load Grant Value<br/>ICP_Grant_Value = PF Load"]
        STEP2["Step 2: Apply Vesting<br/>Per tranche: Grant × Vest%"]
        STEP3["Step 3: RoR Compounding<br/>Value_t = Value_(t-1) × (1+RoR)<br/>PI vs Total Fund split"]
        STEP4["Step 4: Unvested Calc<br/>Grant × (1 - Cum_Vest%) × (1+RoR)^n"]
        STEP5["Step 5: Forfeiture Adj<br/>Unvested × Forfeiture_Rate"]
        STEP6["Step 6: Net ICP Cost<br/>Vested + Unvested + RoR_Adj - Forfeiture"]
        
        STEP1 --> STEP2 --> STEP3 --> STEP4 --> STEP5 --> STEP6
    end

    subgraph VDIP_CALC["🔧 VDIP Calculation"]
        V1["VDIP Accrual<br/>Base × Perf_Factor × Proration"]
        V2["VDIP Payout<br/>Deferred schedule (3-yr)"]
        V3["VDIP Net Cost<br/>Accrual - Payout"]
        V1 --> V3
        V2 --> V3
    end

    subgraph AGG["📤 Aggregation to WFP Cube"]
        EMP_AGG["Employee → Position<br/>Mapping"]
        POS_ICP["ICP_Cost_Loaded<br/>= Σ ICP_Net_Cost<br/>(all employees in position)"]
        POS_VDIP["VDIP_Cost_Loaded<br/>= Σ VDIP_Net_Cost<br/>(all employees in position)"]
        WFP_LOAD["→ WFP Cube<br/>Deferred_Comp accounts"]
    end

    GRANT --> STEP1
    VEST_SCH --> STEP2
    ROR --> STEP3
    FORF --> STEP5

    STEP6 --> EMP_AGG
    V3 --> EMP_AGG
    EMP_AGG --> POS_ICP
    EMP_AGG --> POS_VDIP
    POS_ICP --> WFP_LOAD
    POS_VDIP --> WFP_LOAD

    classDef input fill:#3498DB,stroke:#2C3E50,color:#FFF
    classDef calc fill:#E74C3C,stroke:#C0392B,color:#FFF
    classDef vdip fill:#F39C12,stroke:#E67E22,color:#FFF
    classDef agg fill:#27AE60,stroke:#1E8449,color:#FFF

    class GRANT,VEST_SCH,ROR,FORF input
    class STEP1,STEP2,STEP3,STEP4,STEP5,STEP6 calc
    class V1,V2,V3 vdip
    class EMP_AGG,POS_ICP,POS_VDIP,WFP_LOAD agg
```

