## Diagram 7: Scenario & Version Lifecycle

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Working : Create New Version

    Working --> Working : Planner Edits
    Working --> Final : Submit for Review
    
    Final --> Working : Rejected (Revise)
    Final --> Board_Approved : Approved by Board
    
    Board_Approved --> [*] : Archived (Immutable)

    state Working {
        [*] --> Editing
        Editing --> Calculating : Run Calcs
        Calculating --> Reviewing : Self-Review
        Reviewing --> Editing : Revise
        Reviewing --> Ready : Ready to Submit
    }

    state Final {
        [*] --> Under_Review
        Under_Review --> Approved : Reviewer Approves
        Under_Review --> Rejected : Reviewer Rejects
    }

    note right of Working
        Access: Read/Write for Planners
        Lock: Unlocked
        Actions: Edit, Calculate, Copy
    end note

    note right of Final
        Access: Read-Only for Planners
        Lock: Locked
        Actions: Review, Approve/Reject
    end note

    note right of Board_Approved
        Access: Read-Only for All
        Lock: Permanently Locked
        Actions: View, Report, Compare
    end note
```

